# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Run-specific / internal chunk configurations and reports
# Not included in general public releases — keep local or in a private fork.
#
# Rule of thumb: track templates / scripts / READMEs that are reusable; ignore
# anything that embeds internal bucket URIs, per-workflow IDs, or runtime logs.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
wdl/chunk_0001_0500/
wdl/fg3_input_sumstats_mqq/*.calibration_qc.inputs.json
wdl/fg3_input_sumstats_mqq/*.cromwell_workflow_options.json
wdl/fg3_input_sumstats_mqq/SUBMISSION_REPORT*.md
wdl/fg3_input_sumstats_mqq/submit_all_chunks.log*
wdl/smoke_test/smoke_2files.calibration_qc.inputs.json
wdl/smoke_test/smoke_2files.cromwell_workflow_options.json
wdl/smoke_test/SUBMISSION_REPORT*.md

